![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6234a89c-693e-48e7-88c7-9bb1735c5787/20240830_182344.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_CARMELO HAYES DEF. ANDRADE_**
    

Their fourth match on Smackdown and it's the fastest paved yet. Both men know each other very well, making for some very cool counter spots. Hayes wins this one.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eb3aaa6a-f71d-49f9-9beb-8c2e96905b60/20240830_185749.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_STREET FIGHT: NIA JAX DEF. MICHIN TO RETAIN THE WWE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP_**
    

Tiffany Stratton runs out to get involved and almost cashed in on Nia Jax but Nia caught her red handed. BAYLEY then makes her return to Smackdown for the first time since SummerSlam to fight Tiffy off.